cityinfo.regiowikiText:
RegioWikiAT is a wiki focused on writing about topics
 that only have very local relevance
 This includes for example local brass instrument groups (Blasmusikkapellen)
 or local events in your village.
 You can register on RegiowikiAT and write about these topics right away!
cityinfo.unescoText: Here you can contribute to the entries in the list Intangible Cultural Heritage in Austria (German only). These entries are termed elements by the Austrian Commission for UNESCO. By contributions we mean photos, videos and audio files for each element, including fresh as well as archive material.
feedback.legal:
In principle, to send feedback with this form it isn't necessary to enter any personal data.
 Any personal data entered (e.g. your e-mail if you want reply) will be kept for the duration of the competition and will be deleted thereafter.
We will use your feedback to adopt the data in wikipedia, wikidata or commons and to improve documentation. You will find more information on the privacy policy of Wikimedia Ã–sterreich at https://wikimedia.at/impressum-datenschutz/ (German).
